# Azure Deployment Plan for calculator-web Project

## Goal

Provision and deploy `calculator.web` to Azure using `azcli` + `Bicep` on Azure Container Apps.

## Project Information

- AppName: `calculator-web`
- Stack: `.NET 10`, ASP.NET Core Blazor Server
- Type: Interactive server-side web app
- Project Path: `programming/dotnet/csharp/workspace/calculator-xunit-testing/calculator.web`
- Dependencies: Project reference to `calculator.library`; no external runtime service dependencies detected
- Hosting: Azure Container Apps
- Subscription: `97faaaf2-cb3e-4a96-ae05-335a2fc0eacd`
- Resource Group: `rg-calculator-app`

## Azure Resources Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
svc["calculator-web (.NET 10 Blazor Server)"] --> ca["Azure Container App: calculator-web"]
ca --> cae["Azure Container Apps Environment: cae-calculator-web"]
ca --> acr["Azure Container Registry: acr* (Basic)"]
ca --> uami["User Assigned Managed Identity: uami-calculator-web"]
cae --> law["Log Analytics Workspace: law-calculator-web"]
uami --> acrpull["AcrPull role on ACR"]
```

- The container app pulls images from Azure Container Registry.
- The managed identity is used for ACR pull without admin credentials.
- Container Apps environment sends logs to a shared Log Analytics workspace.

## Recommended Azure Resources

Application `calculator-web`:

- Hosting Service Type: Azure Container Apps
- SKU: Consumption profile, scale-to-zero capable, supports HTTP ingress and autoscale
- Configuration:
  - Language: `dotnet`
  - Environment Variables:
    - `ASPNETCORE_URLS=http://+:8080`
    - `ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT=Production`
  - Dockerfile: `programming/dotnet/csharp/workspace/calculator-xunit-testing/calculator.web/Dockerfile`
  - Docker Context: `programming/dotnet/csharp/workspace/calculator-xunit-testing`
- Dependencies Resource:
  - Azure Container Registry (Basic)
  - Log Analytics Workspace (PerGB2018)
  - User-Assigned Managed Identity
  - Connection Type: Managed Identity

## Recommended Supporting Services

- Application Insights (optional, can be added after base deployment)
- User-Assigned Managed Identity
- Log Analytics Workspace
- Container Registry

## Recommended Security Configurations

- Use managed identity for ACR pull (no registry admin user auth).
- Assign `AcrPull` role definition `7f951dda-4ed3-4680-a7ca-43fe172d538d` to managed identity at ACR scope.
- Keep secrets out of source code; use Key Vault if external dependencies are added later.

## Execution Steps

- [x] Create Dockerfile for `calculator.web`
- [x] Generate Bicep template at `infra/bicep/main.bicep`
- [x] Create deploy script at `scripting/azure/deploy-calculator-web-containerapp.ps1`
- [x] Run deploy script to provision infra and deploy app
- [x] Validate app endpoint and summarize result
